  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Permits Tiverton to require two parking space for each studio, one-bedroom, or two-bedroom low- or moderate-income housing units upon the determination that limited or no local public transportation or off-street parking availability near these units."
